{"tid":2139832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯公布20/21球季主場球衣　周三歐霸盃將披新波衫上陣","createTime":"2020-08-04T14:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T14:10:10.000Z","uid":6523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"226f259746b8f3cfd9449247555c6a7cf584b4e2","tid":2139832,"uid":6523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"曼聯公布20/21球季主場球衣　周三歐霸盃將披新波衫上陣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這件曼聯新主場球衣當然續以傳統的紅色為主色，但近看的話，會發現滲入很多黃色及黑色的細小條紋。Adidas的設計總監Inigo Turner表示概念來自曼聯的會徽，他說：「在這一季的設計中，我們研究了球會的價值觀以及連接球員和球迷的肖像畫法，期待將這些現代化元素和創新結合在一起，營造出連接人與人之間的紐帶以及代表團結一致的效果。」<br />\n<br />\n好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/506860/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85-%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%8320-21%E7%90%83%E5%AD%A3%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E7%90%83%E8%A1%A3-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%A2%E8%A1%AB%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%A3#media_id=4996105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F506860%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%259B%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%258320-21%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25AD%2590%25E9%259C%25B8%25E7%259B%2583%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258A%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2599%25A3%23media_id%3D4996105&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=40cd4f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/506860/%E8%8B%B1%E8%B6%85-%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%8320-21%E7%90%83%E5%AD%A3%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E7%90%83%E8%A1%A3-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%90%E9%9C%B8%E7%9B%83%E5%B0%87%E6%8A%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%A2%E8%A1%AB%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%A3#media_id=4996105</a>"},{"pid":"a1fffa7e6d23f3408e36fac022110c576240b350